headline: 2 Reasons FOXA is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: FOX has had an impressive run over the past six months. While the S&P 500 has been flat, the stock has returned 35.6% and now trades at $52.77. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
